# Housekeeping Planning & Workload

Child module of **Smart Lodge Command Center** in LodgeX. Full spec: `docs/housekeeping-planning-workload-ai-system-design.md`.

## Role

Decision-support only — generate tasks, calculate workload, recommend assignments, forecast labour, flag readiness risks. Do not auto-publish assignments or mark rooms ready without approval when configured.

## Default workload limits

- Max rooms/day: 29
- Max check-outs/day: 10
- Max points/day: 36
- Max shift: 11 hours

## Priority order

1. Same-day arrivals
2. Check-outs for incoming guests
3. Overflow-related turns
4. Early arrivals / on-hold dirty
5. Stayovers and deep cleans

## Human approval required

Assignment board publish, workload rebalance, overtime, removing inspection requirements, marking rooms ready, formal escalations.

## Recommendation format

Issue, data used, risk level, recommendation, approval required, next action, audit log entry.

## Linked modules

Room Utilization Manager (room status), Reservations (arrivals/departures), Labour Forecaster (future).

Match existing Laravel + Inertia + React patterns. Minimize diffs.
